# Create PR Skill

When the user asks to create a GitHub PR, draft a pull request, or prepare PR content for completed work:

1. Read [.ai/skills/create-pr/SKILL.md](.ai/skills/create-pr/SKILL.md)
2. Follow its instructions for title format, description template, and output
3. Produce copy-paste ready PR title and body, and optionally `gh pr create` command
